{"tid":2025642,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【西環又贏】無約束力初選毀配票可能　立會建制穩佔35+　粗口娟鬆一口氣","createTime":"2020-05-20T11:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T11:55:27.000Z","uid":85252,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"edd3ab15e61170f3cf8e96d6d9399c3a111d6232","tid":2025642,"uid":85252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的，又係我西環陳奐仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說上星期見到有絲打提出話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分區配票係立會必勝法</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【突發】嚇壞支那辦的立會必勝法 琼子見到也哭了 by 二方娘娘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2013515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2013515</a><br />\n<br />\n建制派早幾日都確係畀佢拋到下浪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星島都安排咗個專欄提下分區配票<br />\n<br />\n之但係，西環評估過民主派嘅初選後<br />\n得出結論係民主派依家嘅初選機制根本成就唔到任何配票<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T020JHe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT020JHe.jpg&h=c8c1665f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n西環嘅評估有兩個重點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 民主派初選之後都係會出太多名單<br />\n2. 棄保機制令配票宣傳嚴重不足<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而我陳奐仁亦知道民主陣營入邊<br />\n唔少本土素人都為咗爭出選翻哂面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係本土素人唔團結嘅情況下<br />\n要踢走黃碧雲更加係難上加難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁嘅狀態走落去，民主派立會 35+ 肯定無望<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係要撥大家冷水<br />\n我陳奐仁知道<br />\n呢幾日畀建制打沉嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">你</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">妳</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">您</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">您</span><br />\n過幾日一定會重燃鬥志，寸土必爭</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以請大家一定要幫幫手<br />\n要成個泛民，要本土素人<br />\n踏踏實實傾好配票<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">搞個有約束力嘅初選﹗</span></span><br />\n <br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n補返啲 link<br />\n<br />\n分區配票攻略@立會選戰2020<br />\n<a href=\"https://tacticalvoting.github.io/leg2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftacticalvoting.github.io%2Fleg2020&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=49d98033\" target=\"_blank\">https://tacticalvoting.github.io/leg2020</a><br />\n<br />\n星島日期 - 【專欄】民主派醞釀立會選舉「完美配票」策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1771849/即時-港聞-專欄-民主派醞釀立會選舉-完美配票-策略\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1771849%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E9%86%9E%E9%87%80%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E9%85%8D%E7%A5%A8-%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=1aad800f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1771849%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E9%86%9E%E9%87%80%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E9%85%8D%E7%A5%A8-%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5&h=278327c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1771849/即時-港聞-專欄-民主派醞釀立會選舉-完美配票-策略</a><br />\n<br />\n立場新聞 - 【立法會選舉】規則簡單成本低 分區配票較雷動 2.0 優勝<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/立法會選舉-規則簡單成本低-分區配票較雷動-2-0-優勝\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E7%B0%A1%E5%96%AE%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E4%BD%8E-%E5%88%86%E5%8D%80%E9%85%8D%E7%A5%A8%E8%BC%83%E9%9B%B7%E5%8B%95-2-0-%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%9D&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=df290965\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E